cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.HC 

This paper deals with video indexing and semantic search in large-scale video archives, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning methods for training visual concept classifiers, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the study involves human annotators and their agreement, which relates to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Finally, the paper deals with historical video data, which could fall under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
